{
  "stem": "6016.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like a source of the income going into the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was people come in and exchange food for labor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And I did some too, some work, fixing nylons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not nylons, but silk stockings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When they have the runs, there is a special needle to pick it up and to, not to sew them away, but to fix them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was a very tedious work, and I did it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anti-Semitism, especially, personally myself, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know that we didn't go close-- oh yes, in school I remember when we had to, we had to stand up when the Christians said their prayers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had our hands together, and we stood up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't remember exactly whether I was-- in my years, no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to, I used to hear the word Jew, especially on Passover, that when they say that we used to put in the blood into the matzos.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I wouldn't say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I had this a friend that was not Jewish, a personal friend.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think after the war, I, I contacted her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She sent me a picture, her picture, to Paris even, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But recently, I didn't hear from her, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the, [SIGHS] when the war broke out in 1939, in September or August, yeah, we were-- we knew that there was the persecution of Jews.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to go to work for the German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing too serious yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I personally was not alert or aware of it yet, until later on when it was-- when they caught my brother to-- well, it was at night, knocking at the door, coming in--",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we used to, they call it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
